data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Bokeelia! This stunning single-family home boasts three spacious bedrooms, two luxurious bathrooms, and a two-car garage. The highlight of this home is the in-ground pool, perfect for those hot summer days. The kitchen features beautiful granite counters and sleek white appliances, making it a chef's dream. The wood flooring throughout the home adds a touch of elegance and warmth. The icing on the cake is the brand new roof, ensuring that you won't have to worry about any costly repairs for years to come. This home is perfect for families who love to entertain, with plenty of space for guests to relax and enjoy. The open floor plan allows for easy flow between the living room, dining room, and kitchen. The bedrooms are spacious and offer plenty of natural light, making them the perfect place to unwind after a long day. The location of this home is unbeatable, with easy access to all the amenities that Bokeelia has to offer. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning home your own!
